heaviest_rainrate.status: Today, the rain fell at an intense rate peaking at 11.8mm per hour, one of the heaviest downpours recorded and ranked 5th from our records.  The precipitation lasted 2.1 hours and dumped 7.28mm in total.  A torrential downpour occurred on 02 September 2025 when the rain reached a maximum intensity of 27.0mm per hour.
